# CoNiche

CoNiche provides tools to estimate niche position and niche width using:
- CCA / partial-CCA workflows
- GAM fits along single gradients
- Levins niche breadth metrics

## Installation (development)

```r
# install.packages("pak")
# pak::pak("YOUR_GITHUB/CoNiche")
```

## Quick start

See `vignettes/coniche-workflow.Rmd` after building the package.
